cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is about the analysis of stochastic momentum methods for training deep neural networks. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper focuses on convergence rates and generalization performance of deep learning models. However, the paper also involves numerical optimization (cs.NA), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS) in the context of deep learning.
